org.apache.commons.logging.impl
Class SLF4JLog

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.commons.logging.impl.SLF4JLog
All Implemented Interfaces:
Log
public class SLF4JLog
extends Object
implements Log

Implementation of org.apache.commons.logging.Log interface which delegates all processing to a wrapped org.slf4j.Logger instance.

JCL's FATAL and TRACE levels are mapped to ERROR and DEBUG respectively. All other levels map one to one.

Author:
Ceki Gülcü
